data.description: Discover your dream home in the prestigious and serene community of Twin Spires Plantation. This elegant property boasts a nearly half-acre lot (flood zone x) and a host of modern amenities, including a 5-year-old HVAC system, Kevlar hurricane shutters, solar power and a screened in pool with a new liner. Enjoy all the benefits of an HOA without high fees; only $25/month! Its prime location offers easy access to Mobile Highway and Beulah Road. Make the space your own with new flooring and fresh paint; this house has endless potential!  Inside, the house dazzles with high ceilings, custom crown molding, and a triple sliding glass door that bathes the space in natural light. The layout is thoughtfully designed with an open/split bedroom floor plan and features a gas fireplace in the main living area. The kitchen is a chef's delight with a breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances, built-in wall oven, and glass cooktop. The master suite is a luxurious retreat with his and her walk-in closets, dual vanities, and a whirlpool tub. This house also features a Jack and Jill bathroom, perfect for guests and children alike.  Extra storage or workspace is available in the 12’ x 16’ partially insulated detached office built in 2022. Additionally, the home is located just half a mile from the Equestrian Center, adding to its appeal for outdoor enthusiasts.
